hat moment\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 964}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When someone asks me what happened in Rio in 20 years' time, that's my story.\\\"\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 1044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1004, \"end\": 1007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9321084980190094e-15, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"20 years' time\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1025}, {\"ngram\": \"my story\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1042}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When troubled people seethe with hatred, gunning each other down in Rio de Janeiro's favelas, stabbing fellow passengers on European trains and plowing through families on the seafront in Nice, France, with a 19-ton truck, it is genuinely comforting that 11,400 athletes from 205 nations can still come together for two weeks of Olympic competition and treat each other with such respect.\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1114, \"end\": 1128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.229718003842103e-31, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 1234, \"end\": 1238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nice\", \"score\": 0.9999999756810215, \"rank\": 2.4319251007558662e-08, \"text\": \"Nice\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nice\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nice\"}, {\"begin\": 1240, \"end\": 1246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9995732792457187, \"rank\": 0.000426419183149814, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q47